{"tid":2084695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"20190630 新聞 教大女生墮樓亡 遺言籲港人堅持抗爭","createTime":"2020-06-29T11:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T11:53:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"595f4f1087855dc2edbad0e5a444117a53303cf1","tid":2084695,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190630/20716869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716869&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTfuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=a1111bcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716869&h=5e25b438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190630/20716869</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教大女生墮樓亡 遺言籲港人堅持抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/a0502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2Fa0502a.gif&h=378dcee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者墮斃的大廈梯間牆壁寫有反送中控訴。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名大學女生昨午在粉嶺嘉福邨福泰樓墮斃，家人傷心欲絕。女生墮樓前在大廈梯間牆壁用紅筆留言作出反送中控訴，<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n21歲死者姓盧，為教育大學文化與創意藝術學系音樂系的二年級學生，與父母與胞妹居於上水，盧父昨晚表示，女兒性格乖巧，成績好考獲獎學金，對她突然墮樓身亡感難以接受，家人不知道她有否參與遊行，盧母則泣不成聲。據悉，盧女有情緒病紀錄，近日曾因感情問題與男友爭執。死者一名學長對《蘋果》表示，盧女有參與最近反送中遊行及集會，但未有通宵留守，行為亦未見激進，前晚還相約數個朋友聚餐，當時她毫無異樣，亦沒有談及對反送中的看法，詎料發生慘劇。<br />\n<br />\n昨午3時許，盧女被發現昏迷倒卧嘉福邨福泰樓對開地面，救護員到場證實不治，警方封鎖現場調查，發現大廈24樓梯間牆上有死者署名、用紅筆寫上反送中及近一百字的文章，內容提及「雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去，強烈要求全面撤回條例，收回暴動論，釋放學生示威者，林鄭下台，嚴懲警方，本人但願可以小命，成功換取二百萬人的心願，請你們堅持下去」，然後將相片上載至個人Instagram，有朋友追問其安危但未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政府違諾拒開放軍用碼頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30la4p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30la4p11.jpg&h=118b9763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少市民昨晚到場獻花悼念。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/a0502b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2Fa0502b.gif&h=b902c904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩：唔可以再失去任何人<br />\n<br />\n警方以黑<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n：「大家應承我，照顧自己，留喺度一齊走落去，我哋唔可以再失去任何一個人。」教育大學發言人表示，對事件感震驚和悲慟，校方已啟動危機處理機制。教大學生會在fb發帖，「致盧同學：你未走完的路，我們會走下去&hellip;&hellip;」該會今日下午將在大埔校園中央廣場舉行悼念儀式。<br />\n<br />\n港大防止自殺研究中<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫文學 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n政府違諾拒開放軍用碼頭<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n明日上街 撤惡法撤林鄭"},{"pid":"2ebda00b2ea529b405d1dbc1f0fbc91657819b48","tid":2084695,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWsavmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWsavmb.jpg&h=cd1318a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMZoGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMZoGd.jpg&h=a6ae71e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1GZoGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1GZoGe.jpg&h=0d4591f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z00joGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz00joGf.jpg&h=4056509e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yv6Og1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYv6Og1f.jpg&h=64a33f35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJwys7W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJwys7W.jpg&h=e60c0bee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/revO1sX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrevO1sX.jpg&h=0b789d25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6J2qjeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6J2qjeC.jpg&h=31e5fca3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}